{"comments":"HWB - Hue, Whiteness, Blackness (CSS Color Level 4).\n\n**MORE INTUITIVE THAN HSL:**\nInstead of saturation and lightness, HWB uses:\n- How much white is mixed in (whiteness)\n- How much black is mixed in (blackness)\n\n**Components:**\n- **H**: Hue, 0-360 degrees (color wheel position)\n- **W**: Whiteness, 0-100% (amount of white mixed in)\n- **B**: Blackness, 0-100% (amount of black mixed in)\n\n**Use cases:**\n- CSS4 hwb() function\n- More intuitive color picking for designers\n- \"Make it lighter\" = increase whiteness\n- \"Make it darker\" = increase blackness\n\n**CSS Example:**\nhwb(120deg 20% 10%) - green with 20% white, 10% black\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","HWB"],"HWB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[109,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/HWB.purs","start":[109,1]},"title":"eqHWB"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","HWB"],"HWB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[110,34],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/HWB.purs","start":[110,1]},"title":"ordHWB"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","HWB"],"HWB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[113,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/HWB.purs","start":[112,1]},"title":"showHWB"}],"comments":"HWB color - composition of Hue, Whiteness, Blac